<div type="definition">
<p>COMPETE with OTHERS USING the LAW.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The general word for any lawsuit one person takes out against another is sòng 訟.</p>
<p>2. Yù 獄 typically refers specifically to a criminal lawsuit.</p>
        </div>
<div type="huang-jingui">
<p>HUANG JINGUI 2006</p>
<p>GOVERNMENT AND LAW 36. 訴訟。</p>
<p>訴，將自己所受的不平之事告訴司法部門，最早出現於漢代。</p>
<p>訟，對仲裁人告訴并爭辯彼此的是非曲直。</p>
<p>告，主動告訴他人的犯罪言行，春秋戰國時已見。</p>
<p>發，將他人隱蔽的犯罪言行告訴有關部門。</p>
        </div>
